Agree. A good friend or mentor is a blessing but some times you cannot share noncoherent but hurtful or embarrassing thoughts and experiences to even your mentor. But you can always talk to Allah  no matter how stupid the things you are saying. Easiest way to get clarity and repel depression is to write down whatever is coming in your mind preferably hand writen but typing is fine too. After worrisom thoughts you start getting guiding thoughts and it makes all that fog of worries/ confusion disappear or manageable.
